text: Ic Osuuald þurh Godes giefe arcebisceop mid geþafunge & leafe Eadwardes Angulcyningæs & Ælfheres Mercna heretogan & þæs heorodes æt Wygerneceastre landes sumne dæl þæt is an hid æt Witlea sumum preoste þam is Wulfgar noma mid allum þingum þe þarto belimpað freolice his dæge forgeaf & æfter his dæge twam yrfweardum & æfter hieora forðsiþe to þære halgan stowe into Wiogornaceastre þæm biscope to bryce.
Sit autem terra ista libera omni regi nisi ecclesiastici censi.
Sancta Maria & Sanctus Michahel cum sancto Petro& allum Godes halgum gemiltsien þis haldendum.
Gief hwa buton gewrihtum hit abrecan wille hæbbe him wið God gemæne on þam ytemestan dæge þisses lifes buton he ær to dædbote gecyrre.
Þis sindon þæs landes gemæra þe gebyriað into þære westmestan hide æt Witleage, feldlondes & wudulandes swa hit todæled is.
Of ðrym gemæran westrihte on þa dic.
Andlang weges on þa hæþihtan leage & swa on þæt fule sloh.
Of þæm slo ofer buttingc graf on eccles broc.
